-- Ukraine Seeks to Buy Gas From Europe’s Spot Market, Zerkalo Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-03-12T08:56:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/ukraine-seeks-to-buy-gas-from-europe-s-spot-market-zerkalo-says.html
Ukraine’s state-owned energy
company NAK Naftogaz Ukrainy plans to sign a short-term contract
with  RWE AG (RWE)  to supply about 3 million cubic meters of natural
gas a day via pipelines in Slovakia, the  Zerkalo Nedeli  weekly
reported, citing documents it obtained.  Gas will be bought on the spot market in  Europe , Kiev-based
Zerkalo reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina  in Kiev at 
